annotationA: Mitochondrial ribosomal protein L46; Structural constituent of ribosome; hydrolase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitochondrial translation
annotationB: 3-hydroxyisobutyryl-CoA hydrolase, mitochondrial; Hydrolyzes 3-hydroxyisobutyryl-CoA (HIBYL-CoA), a saline catabolite; Belongs to the enoyl-CoA hydratase/isomerase family
